{"data":{"page":{"id":"519228af-e7d6-501b-8f94-82b7a6a75d28","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2bd228d3e1a12a4b5082c1b83bf6abd5/877ff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2bd228d3e1a12a4b5082c1b83bf6abd5/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2bd228d3e1a12a4b5082c1b83bf6abd5/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/2bd228d3e1a12a4b5082c1b83bf6abd5/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>As part of my partnership with Esuma, where I also was a teacher in one of their master programs, I built a Joomla website for the institution. It features a login area with private pages for the students and teachers and other static pages with content related with the educational offer and latest news.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2009"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ESUMA website","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/0160d4b4c4d007786f9e77fd32976f64/d927d/logo.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/esuma/","source":"work"}}